<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١١٤⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5027">عِيسَى بْنِ يُونُسَ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2638">الْأَعْمَشِ </a>بِهَذَا الْإِسْنَادِ مِثْلَهُ،<span class="c5"> غَيْرَ أَنَّهُ يَقُولُ:</span> إِنْ سَرَقَ حَبْلًا وَإِنْ سَرَقَ بَيْضَةً .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>